text: Gabriela Grzywińska (born 18 February 1996) is a Polish footballer who plays as a midfielder and has appeared for the Poland women's national team. ==Career== Grzywińska has been capped for the Poland national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Polish women's footballers Category:Poland women's international footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Medyk Konin players
